  "content": "GIN GINS® GINGER CANDY The Ginger Candy That Started It All GIN GINS® set the standard for ginger candy with more fresh ginger than any other candy brand and the bold, unmistakable flavor ginger lovers crave. Known for leading the category in digestive comfort, GIN GINS combines real functional ginger with a satisfying candy experience unlike ordinary sweets POPULAR FOR: DIGESTIVE COMFORT, MOTION DISCOMFORT AND TRAVEL, CHEMOTHERAPY SUPPORT ROUTINES, ROAD TRIPS AND BOATING, RUNNING, SINGING AND EVERYDAY GINGER ENJOYMENT. GIN GINS® Original Ginger Chews GIN GINS® Boost – Red Magic Ginger Chews GIN GINS® Mandarin Orange Ginger Chews GIN GINS® Lemon Ginger Chews GIN GINS® Spicy Apple Ginger Chews GIN GINS® Peanut Ginger Chews GIN GINS® Spicy Turmeric Ginger Chews GIN GINS® Double Strength Hard Ginger Candy GIN GINS® Super Strength Ginger Candy GIN GINS® Ginger Spice Drops GIN GINS® Sweet Ginger Gummies",
